name: Admin Console Release 25.10.7
description: The following release of the LoginRadius Admin Console brings you some new features. See below for details on some of the more notable changes applied to the Admin Console.

ADDED.text: The existing Webhook can now be edited without being unsubscribed. Additionally, you can add the Custom Object directly in the Webhook form available in the Admin Console.
Now Audit Logs will have the entries of team memberâ€™s addition and deletion activities.
The Auth-Common JS file can be edited using the 'Common Script' option in the deployment->IDX section of the Admin Console.
